---
title: Chicken Tikka Masala with Carrots and Garlic Rice
description: Bold tikka masala and cream coat tender chicken and sweet carrots in this quick and easy curry! The aromas will make you want to dig in before this hits the table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-tikka-masala-aa57ee23.jpg
